name: Wall Street Pepe
description: Wall Street Pepe ($WEPE) is a meme-based cryptocurrency inspired by internet culture, specifically targeting the 'degen' crypto audience. It features a decentralized exchange (DEX) launch, meme-driven branding, and staking rewards. Designed to appeal to fans of meme coins and the 'Pepe' character, the project emphasizes community and humor in its approach.
